name: AyoniMix Anime
description:
Made a more anime/illustrative version of my other mix. Responds much better to most LORAs, HNs, and embeds on this site, as they are mostly anime themed.

No LORAs, HN, or embeds used in example images. Used SD 1.5 VAE.

modelVersions.name: AyoniMix Anime V4
modelVersions.description: I've neglected the anime verison for too long. Clipfixed, and noise offset adjusted.
